Š[{"URL":"/image/3f06d6d3b75de6ca768f4a2a9768d2848171ba4f","importURL":"https://www.flickr.com/photos/31047857@N00/4384555350","licence":"CC BY-NC-ND 2.0","media_type":"inscription","sha1":"3f06d6d3b75de6ca768f4a2a9768d2848171ba4f","width":3888,"height":2592},{"URL":"/image/6f840c39adefcfb9859addd2da17100a6d50e2a7","licence":"CC BY-SA 4.0","media_type":"inscription","sha1":"6f840c39adefcfb9859addd2da17100a6d50e2a7","width":4608,"height":3456}]"┼
┬As a small boy not far from this very spot, he began running and did not stop
Far across the globe he ran, this beloved, crazy, brilliant man
He loved wine. music and the southern sun, he always gave his best to everyone
He is much missed and that he should, for our south London boy did good
Vincent Hancock 1944-2006"▄
